(A) \rangle\rightarrow|2,1,0\rangle\rightarrow|1,0,0\rangle  and \frac{2}{3}
(B) |3,0,0\rangle\rightarrow|2,1,0\rangle\rightarrow|1,0,0\rangle and \frac{1}{3}
